181
00:10:55,322 --> 00:10:57,698
Everything just disappear.

182
00:10:57,740 --> 00:11:00,827
All the bad feeling
disappear, and now

183
00:11:00,828 --> 00:11:02,078
"Oh, are you married?"

184
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,722
You know, "How many
children do you have?"

185
00:11:03,746 --> 00:11:05,706
