225
00:13:01,656 --> 00:13:02,841
This is my favorite,
favorite restaurant.

226
00:13:02,865 --> 00:13:04,618
- This place?
- Yes.

227
00:13:04,659 --> 00:13:06,661
The name comes from
the owner, this lady,

228
