288
00:16:07,049 --> 00:16:10,010
♪

289
00:16:16,434 --> 00:16:18,018
A story all its own.

290
00:16:18,060 --> 00:16:22,064
Lives lived, being lived,
caught for a second,

291
00:16:22,106 --> 00:16:25,067
a moment, then gone.

