00:16:27,528 --> 00:16:30,615
In Vietnam sometime,
to be truly friend,

293
00:16:30,657 --> 00:16:32,826
- to be friendly...
- Yeah.

294
00:16:32,867 --> 00:16:35,035
We have to drink
until we a drunk.

